* From his vantage point Dinobot could see Tavatron slip into the trees and 
go a little ways before the branches blocked out his view.
What did she want him to do, chase her and see if he could track her down?
If that was it then it wouldn't be much of a challenge, unless it was a 
practice Seek And Destroy tactic, which meant that they would track each 
other down and see who can get the drop on whom.
Dinobot looked down the cliff face and nodded to himself, it wasn't to far 
to the bottom of the cliff.
He took a few steps back then jumped from the cliff edge, he landed herd on 
the valley floor but kept on his feet none the less.
Dinobot looked around and at the trees only a few feet away from him and 
sniffed the air, since Tavatron had just entered the forest the trail was 
fresh and wouldn't be difficult to follow. Not for a while anyway, he knew 
that if this was a Seek And Destroy practice battle then Tavatron would hide 
her trail the best she could.
Dinobot snarled as he moved off in a similar direction but slightly off 
Tavatron's trail, he could follow her sent from where he was at without 
being right on her trail.
He moved off into the forest, hunting for Maximal!*
